        Trump says he found $23 billion for Wall from ‘other sources’

    </h1><div class="article__date"><span class="date date_article-header">Published time: 13 Feb, 2019 00:35 </span><span class="date date_article-header">Edited time: 13 Feb, 2019 10:31 </span></div><div class="article__short-url"><div class="short-url"><a class="short-url__link" href="https://on.rt.com/9o8s">Get short URL</a></div></div><div class="article__cover"><div class="media  "><picture><!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]--><source
