                    /></picture><!-- noscript pattern --><noscript><img src="https://cdni.rt.com/files/2019.02/xxs/5c6365dedda4c815118b4589.JPG" class="media__item " alt="Trump says he found $23 billion for Wall from ‘other sources’" /></noscript></div><div class="media__footer media__footer_bottom "><div class="media__title media__title_arcticle"><span data-role="title">President Donald Trump holds a photo of the border wall design at a White House meeting in January 2019 </span><span data-role="copyright-symbol">©&nbsp;</span><span data-role="copyright">                Reuters/Leah Millis</span></div></div></div><div class="article__share"><div class="social-container"
