    </span>
</a><p><em>&ldquo;We&rsquo;re going to build a big, beautiful strong wall,&rdquo;</em> he said earlier in the day, speaking with reporters at the White House. <em>&ldquo;I never kid about construction. I love construction, and I know how to do it for the right price.&rdquo;</em></p><p>Reporters on the ground in El Paso, Texas &ndash; where Trump held a big campaign-style rally on Monday evening &ndash; posted photos of construction crews erecting a barrier made of steel slats where only a chain fence existed before.</p><p><strong><em>Like this story? Share it with a friend!</em></strong></p><p></p></div><div class="article__share"><div class="social-container"
